{
  "name": "Artists",
  "slug": "artists",
  "widgets": {
    "opener": {
      "type": "split-content",
      "settings": {
        "balance": "left-heavy",
        "sticky_column": "none",
        "color_scheme": "standard-primary",
        "top_spacing": "auto",
        "bottom_spacing": "auto"
      },
      "blocks": {
        "op-eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The artists</p>",
            "size": "sm",
            "uppercase": true,
            "muted": true,
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "op-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Six artists. Six hands. Six practices.",
            "size": "7xl",
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "op-body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every resident at Inkwell chose the studio because it let them do their own work. We don't rotate artists through generalist queues — you book the person whose style you want, not a shift. Each artist sets their own pace, pricing, and waiting list. The studio holds the standard for hygiene, consultation, and aftercare.</p>",
            "size": "lg",
            "position": "right"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["op-eyebrow", "op-heading", "op-body"]
    },
    "artist_saoirse": {
      "type": "split-content",
      "settings": {
        "balance": "left-heavy",
        "sticky_column": "right",
        "color_scheme": "standard-primary",
        "top_spacing": "none",
        "bottom_spacing": "auto"
      },
      "blocks": {
        "s-image": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "width": 100,
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "s-label": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Fine line · single-needle · 8 years</p>",
            "size": "sm",
            "uppercase": true,
            "muted": true,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "s-name": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Saoirse Doyle",
            "size": "4xl",
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "s-bio": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Dublin-trained, Brooklyn-based. Saoirse works almost exclusively in single-needle fine line — botanicals, script, portraits, and architectural studies at small scale. Known for extraordinary line consistency and for flowers that actually look like flowers.</p><p>Books two to three months out.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "s-button": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link": {
              "text": "See Saoirse's work",
              "href": "work.html",
              "target": "_self"
            },
            "style": "secondary",
            "size": "medium",
            "alignment": "start",
            "position": "right"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["s-image", "s-label", "s-name", "s-bio", "s-button"]
    },
