            "text": "Elena Stavros",
            "size": "4xl",
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "e-bio": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Photorealistic black-and-grey work — portraits, architectural studies, animal work, old-master-referenced figurative pieces. Elena's sessions are long (six to eight hours) and her bookings are deep.</p><p>A full sleeve typically takes five to seven sittings over six months.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "muted": false,
            "position": "left"
