        "j-bio": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Heavy blackwork drawing on woodcut, etching, and ornament traditions. Jules came to tattooing from printmaking, and it shows in the composition — graphic panels, baroque borders, illustrative beasts.</p><p>Large-scale pieces a speciality.</p>",
