            "text": "<p>Geometric dotwork and mandala-derived ornament — precise, mathematical, deeply patterned. Indra studied architecture before tattooing, which shapes her approach to symmetry and scale.</p><p>Often collaborates with Jules on large ornamental back pieces.</p>",
